defaultThe administration of the aforementioned Acts (and the Zoo Lic
defaultensing Act) 
defaultshould, therefore,
default be removed from Local Authority administration and discharged by central government.  
defaultUntil such time as this happens we shall continue to see inconsistencies and failures in administration of legislation that will compromise
default the welfare of 
defaultboth
default primates but other species.
